VALUES
  ('medical-tech-moex-07958', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-106-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於flucytosine類抗黴菌藥物之敘述，何者正確？', '["flucytosine與amphotericin B有加成作用，因此可合併使用治療念珠菌造成之全身性感染", "作用機轉是抑制14α-去甲基酶", "flucytosine是目前唯一真正具有殺菌效果之口服抗黴菌藥物", "可造成細胞內squalene（一種毒物）之堆積，其對於各種皮癬菌之MIC值特別低"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8e4a65d4b75e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1b85c79554b6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106020", "c": "308", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、藥師、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 55, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-07959', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-106-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '院內感染管制中，對於上呼吸道的感染，最常從病人的鼻孔分離出下列何種菌？', '["Mycobacterium avium complex", "Staphylococcus aureus", "Vibrio parahaemolyticus", "Treponema pallidum"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8e4a65d4b75e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1b85c79554b6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106020", "c": "308", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、藥師、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 56, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-07960', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-106-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於厭氧菌（anaerobes）抗生素感受性試驗，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["以瓊脂稀釋法測試，培養基使用Brucella blood agar", "以微量稀釋法測試，培養液可使用Brucella broth或brain-heart infusion broth", "接種後，培養18至24小時後觀察", "以微量稀釋法測試，只適用於Bacteroides fragilis group"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8e4a65d4b75e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1b85c79554b6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106020", "c": "308", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、藥師、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 57, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
